metadata.name: RED.RØS
metadata.description:
Experienced Spectral Botanists scour endless Worlds to  find the RED.RØS, and few that do can hold on to it.

 If mastered, the RED.RØS alchemical properties could greatly imbue one's abilities with superhuman Clairvoyance and Clairalience.

 Also makes for an out of this world perfume essence.
